<%- include('../includes/header', { title: 'About Us' }) %>

<main>
    <section class="about-container">
        <div class="about-content">
            <h1 class="about-title">About Us</h1>
            <p class="about-description">
                Welcome to Bajrang Fitness, the premier destination for achieving your fitness goals and living a healthier life. 
                Founded with the mission to inspire and support individuals on their fitness journey, we offer state-of-the-art gym 
                facilities designed to cater to all levels of fitness enthusiasts. Whether you're a beginner or a seasoned athlete, 
                our gym is equipped with the latest exercise machines, free weights, and functional training areas to help you 
                maximize your workouts.
            </p>
            <p class="about-description">
                Our team of certified trainers and nutrition experts are dedicated to providing personalized guidance and support. 
                From one-on-one personal training sessions to group classes, we offer a variety of programs tailored to meet your 
                specific needs and preferences. Our trainers are not only skilled but passionate about helping you reach your 
                fitness goals, and they are always available to answer your questions and provide motivation.
            </p>
            <p class="about-description">
                At Bajrang Fitness, we also understand the importance of a balanced diet in achieving fitness success. Our in-house 
                nutritionists work closely with our members to create customized meal plans that complement their training routines. 
                We believe in a holistic approach to fitness that encompasses both physical exercise and proper nutrition.
            </p>
            <p class="about-description">
                Our facility features a variety of amenities to enhance your gym experience, including:
            </p>
            <ul class="about-list">
                <li>Modern cardio and strength training equipment</li>
                <li>Dedicated functional training zones</li>
                <li>Refreshing locker rooms with showers</li>
                <li>Wellness and relaxation areas</li>
                <li>Nutrition and supplement shop</li>
                <li>Friendly and supportive community atmosphere</li>
            </ul>
            <p class="about-description">
                We are committed to creating a positive and empowering environment where everyone feels welcome and inspired. 
                Join us at Bajrang Fitness and take the first step towards a healthier, happier you!
            </p>

            <!-- Trainers Section -->
            <section class="trainers-section">
                <h2 class="trainers-title">Meet Our Trainers</h2>
                <div class="trainers-container">
                    <% trainers.forEach(trainer => { %>
                        <div class="trainer-card">
                            <img src="/uploads/<%= trainer.image %>" alt="<%= trainer.name %>" class="trainer-photo">
                            <div class="trainer-info">
                                <h3 class="trainer-name"><%= trainer.name %></h3>
                                <p class="trainer-specialty"><%= trainer.specialty %></p>
                            </div>
                        </div>
                    <% }); %>
                </div>
            </section>
        </div>
    </section>
</main>

<%- include('../includes/footer') %>
